# Machine-REGENERATED output — the generator is the source of truth, not prettier.
# `regenerate.yml` (daily cron) + the generate:* scripts own these; formatting them
# here would fight the generator and produce churn on every refresh.
#   - site/            public rendered HTML (regenerate.py + ingest-render.ts)
#   - site-internal/   tailnet-only operator HTML (generate-internal*.ts)
#   - data/            eval-set source data refreshed by regenerate.py
#   - .ingest-store/   content-addressed verified-bundle store
site/
site-internal/
data/
.ingest-store/

